---

<section id="about" class="py-16 bg-gray-50 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl px-4 mx-auto sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
        Who We Are
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 mx-auto mt-4 bg-yellow-500 rounded"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Block -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p>
        Established in <strong>November 2011</strong>, <span class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">Abhyuday</span> is a premier Project Management Consultancy (PMC) with over a decade of specialized experience in <strong>Agro and Food processing cluster development</strong> and <strong>MoFPI schemes</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        With a nationwide reach across <strong>21+ Indian states</strong>, including the North-East, and a global presence with offices in <strong>Japan, USA, and Africa</strong>, our commitment to excellence is reflected in over <strong>₹5,000 Cr of completed projects</strong> and <strong>₹1,000 Cr in ongoing initiatives</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Grid -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 text-center">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">₹5,000+ Cr</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Completed Projects</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">₹1,000 Cr</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Ongoing Projects</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">21+ States</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Pan-India Presence</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">10+ Years</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">MoFPI & Cluster Expertise</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Global Reach</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Offices in Japan, USA, Africa</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA or Mission -->
    <p class="mt-12 text-center text-base italic text-gray-600">
      Empowering the food processing ecosystem—project by project, globally.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
